    dc:description "FIG. 8. — Spores from the Barremian of south-west Japan: A-C, Retitriletes sp. (A, proximal face, Kimigahama Fm, SEM-I1a; B, lateral view, Kimigahama Fm, SEM-I1a; C, distal face, Kimigahama Fm, SEM-I1c); D, E, H-J, Foveosporites ryosekiensis n. sp. (D, E, proximal and distal faces,Ashikajima Fm,II2a-U63;H, proximal face,Ashikajima Fm,SEM-II2a;I, proximal face,Ashikajima Fm,SEM-II2b;J, lateral" ;
